## 4. File Organization

```
/${domain_name}/
  enums/                 ← READ-ONLY enum definitions
    _schema/             ← Meta-schema
    ${system_a}/         ← Coordinate system A enums
    ${system_b}/         ← Coordinate system B enums
  data/                  ← Coordinate assignments
  engine/                ← Pipeline modules
    audit.py             ← Audit adapter (wraps lazarus.audit)
  experiments/           ← Convergence experiments
  logbook/               ← ONE-WAY reference only (logbook → domain)
```

