## 5. Library Integration

```python
# Install: pip install -e ~/Documents/Lazarus
from lazarus.registry.domain import DomainRegistry

registry = DomainRegistry(
    name="${domain_name}",
    project_root=PROJECT_ROOT,
    schema_dir=PROJECT_ROOT / "enums",
    data_dir=PROJECT_ROOT / "data",
    meta_schema_path=PROJECT_ROOT / "enums/_schema/enum_meta_schema.json",
)

# Use factory methods
auditor1 = registry.build_schema_auditor()
auditor2 = registry.build_boundary_auditor()
convergence = registry.build_categorical_convergence()
```
